<div class="row">
	<div class="span12">
		<h1>Leaderboard</h1>
		<h2>XX Total</h2>
		<p>Donec id neque et libero accumsan imperdiet in et nisl. Curabitur leo metus, viverra et interdum id, interdum sed dui.</p>
		
		<p>
			<%= link_to 'About', about_url, :class => 'btn btn-large' %>
			<span id="start-panel">
				or
				<%= link_to 'Start', leap_url, :class => 'btn btn-large btn-primary' %>
			</span>
		</p>
		
		<table>
		  <tr>
		    <th>Distance</th>
		    <th>Type</th>
		    <th></th>
